'''诺基亚 Lumia 1520'''是[[Nokia|Nokia]]公司设计和生产的一款[[平板手机|平板手机]]，2013年10月22日在[[阿布扎比|阿布扎比]]与 [[Nokia_Lumia_1320|Nokia Lumia 1320]] 和 [[Nokia_Lumia_2520|Nokia Lumia 2520]]一同发布<ref>{{Cite news |author=Griffith, Chris |url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/technology/nokia-announces-its-first-tablet-the-lumia-2520-and-two-6-inch-phablets/story-e6frgakx-1226744848012 |title=Nokia announces its first tablet, the Lumia 2520, and two 6-inch 'phablets' |newspaper=The Australian |date=22 October 2013 |accessdate=25 October 2013 |archive-date=2014-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307235610/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/technology/nokia-announces-its-first-tablet-the-lumia-2520-and-two-6-inch-phablets/story-e6frgakx-1226744848012 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |author=Stroh, Michael |url=http://blogs.windows.com/windows_phone/b/windowsphone/archive/2013/10/22/nokia-unveils-their-first-6-inch-windows-phones-and-a-new-windows-tablet-plus-here-comes-instagram.aspx |title=Nokia goes big, introduces the Lumia 1520 and 1320 with 6-inch HD screens. Plus: Instagram is coming! |work=Windows Blogs |date=22 October 2013 |accessdate=26 October 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029190914/http://blogs.windows.com/windows_phone/b/windowsphone/archive/2013/10/22/nokia-unveils-their-first-6-inch-windows-phones-and-a-new-windows-tablet-plus-here-comes-instagram.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，屏幕尺寸为6英寸，是当今世界上屏幕最大的[[Windows_Phone|Windows Phone]]系统手机，是一款意在与[[Samsung_Galaxy_Note_3|Samsung Galaxy Note 3]]和[[HTC_One_Max|HTC One Max]]竞争的手机<ref name=NextWeb>[http://thenextweb.com/gadgets/2013/10/22/official-nokia-lumia-1520/ Nokia Lumia 1520 Hands-On] {{Wayback|url=http://thenextweb.com/gadgets/2013/10/22/official-nokia-lumia-1520/ |date=20140101091759 }}. Thenextweb.com. Retrieved on 22 October 2013.</ref>。

== 供货 ==
Lumia 1520首发的国家和地区有新加坡、香港、美国、法国、中国、德国、芬兰和印度。Lumia 1520在澳大利亚由{{link-en|哈维诺曼|Harvey Norman}}独家做为合约机销售<ref>{{Cite web  |author=Harvey Norman AU  |url=http://www.harveynorman.com.au/homepage/nokia-lumia-1520-windows-8-phone.html  |title=Lumia 1520 Availabe  |deadurl=yes  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219112718/http://www.harveynorman.com.au/homepage/nokia-lumia-1520-windows-8-phone.html  |archivedate=2013-12-19  |access-date=2014-01-11  }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |author=Nermin Bajric |url=http://www.arnnet.com.au/article/532847/harvey_norman_sell_nokia_lumia_1520_telcos_miss/ |title=Harvey Norman to sell Nokia Lumia 1520 as telcos miss out |work=ARN |date=26 November 2013 |accessdate=14 January 2014 |archive-date=2013-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204201612/http://www.arnnet.com.au/article/532847/harvey_norman_sell_nokia_lumia_1520_telcos_miss/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在美国由[[AT&T|AT&T]]独家销售<ref>{{Cite web |author=Byford, Sam |url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/10/22/4865368/att-to-carry-nokia-lumia-1520-and-2520 |title=AT&T is the exclusive carrier for Nokia's Lumia 1520, will also sell Lumia 2520 tablet |work=The Verge |date=22 October 2013 |accessdate=26 October 2013 |archive-date=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106200811/http://www.theverge.com/2013/10/22/4865368/att-to-carry-nokia-lumia-1520-and-2520 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==设计==
Lumia 1520屏幕材质为IPS LCD<ref>{{cite web|title=Detailed specifications for the Nokia Lumia 1520|url=http://www.nokia.com/us-en/phones/phone/lumia1520/specifications/|publisher=Nokia|accessdate=31 October 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030000831/http://www.nokia.com/us-en/phones/phone/lumia1520/specifications/|archivedate=2013年10月30日}}</ref>，分辨率1080p，是第一款达到此分辨率的WP手机，可以显示3列动态磁贴，屏幕表面覆盖一层[[大猩猩玻璃|大猩猩玻璃]]2 抗刮玻璃。屏幕尺寸为6英寸，像素密度为368ppi<ref name=Engadget>{{Cite web |author=Smith, Mat |url=http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/22/nokia-lumia-1520/ |title=Nokia Lumia 1520: Windows Phone with 6-inch 1080p display and 20MP camera for $750 |work=Engadget |date=22 October 2013 |accessdate=26 October 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022072912/http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/22/nokia-lumia-1520/ |archivedate=2013-10-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |author=Ghos, Shona |url=http://www.pcpro.co.uk/news/384874/nokia-lumia-2520-tablet-arrives-ahead-of-new-ipad |title=Nokia Lumia 2520 tablet arrives ahead of new iPad |work=PC Pro |date=22 October 2013 |accessdate=26 October 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131226032936/http://www.pcpro.co.uk/news/384874/nokia-lumia-2520-tablet-arrives-ahead-of-new-ipad |archive-date=2013-12-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，CPU采用[[骁龙|Snapdragon 800]][[系统芯片|系统芯片]]，频率为 2.2 GHz 。摄像头采用2000万像素的蔡司镜头PureView<ref name=NextWeb/><ref name=FirstTheVerge>{{Cite web|author=Seifert, Dan|url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/10/22/4865276/nokia-world-2013-lumia-phone-announcements|title=Nokia introduces the Lumia 1520, its largest Windows Phone yet|work=The Verge|date=22 October 2013|accessdate=22 October 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022121037/http://www.theverge.com/2013/10/22/4865276/nokia-world-2013-lumia-phone-announcements|archivedate=2013-10-22|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。支持[[4G_LTE|4G LTE]]和[[近场通信|近场通信]]，机身内存为32GB，支持MicroSD储存卡，最大存储扩展为128GB（该手机推出时世界范围内并没有存储量为128GB的MicroSD储存卡，所以说明书上的说明是最大存储扩展64GB）<ref name=Engadget/>。电池容量为3400mAh<ref name=Engadget/>。

与 [[Nokia_Lumia_1020|Nokia Lumia 1020]] 类似，Lumia 1520每次拍照都会存储两张照片，一张为500万像素，用于网络分享，一张为1600万像素，用于计算机处理。<ref name=TheVerge>{{Cite web |author=Warren, Tom |url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/10/22/4862948/nokia-lumia-1520-hands-on-photos-video |title=Nokia Lumia 1520: a first look at a 6-inch giant Windows Phone |work=The Verge |date=22 October 2013 |accessdate=26 October 2013 |archive-date=2014-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111044530/http://www.theverge.com/2013/10/22/4862948/nokia-lumia-1520-hands-on-photos-video |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=搜狐数码|title=Lumia 1520外媒评测|url=http://digi.it.sohu.com/20131120/n390419810.shtml|publisher=搜狐网|accessdate=2014-01-12|archive-date=2014-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140112043621/http://digi.it.sohu.com/20131120/n390419810.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

